overview.en: GTR is the platform currency of the Mcoin trading platform. Gtrhz.com's premier high-quality digital asset trading platform, for the first time, introduces AI technology into digital asset trading, creating a smart cloud system, innovatively realizing transaction security, platform stability, and operational convenience. It is recognized as a global high-quality intelligence. Digital Asset Trading Desk.
overview.zh: GTR是Mcoin交易平台的平台币。gtrhz.com首屈一指的优质数字资产交易平台，首次将AI技术引入数字资产交易，独创智能云系统，创新地实现了交易的安全性、平台的稳定性、操作的便利性，是公认的全球优质智能数字资产交易台。
